{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-8581aaff406c883b", "type": "tool_result", "content": "Usage: paper-wiki [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...\n\n  My Paper Wiki CLI.\n\nOptions:\n  --help  Show this message and exit.\n\nCommands:\n  index   Build indexes.\n  list    List papers or sections.\n  search  Search papers and content.\n---\nUsage: paper-wiki search [OPTIONS]\n\n  Search papers and content.\n\nOptions:\n  -p, --paper TEXT      arXiv ID\n  -s, --section TEXT    Section name\n  -c, --concept TEXT    Search by concept\n  -d, --dataset TEXT    Search by dataset\n  -a, --author TEXT     Search by author\n  -m, --method TEXT     Search by method\n  -f, --fuzzy TEXT      Fuzzy search\n  -b, --bm25 TEXT       BM25 full-text search\n  -t, --tag TEXT        Search by tag\n  --topic TEXT          Search by topic\n  --citations TEXT      Citation graph traversal from arxiv ID\n  --edge-type TEXT      Filter by edge type\n  --depth INTEGER       Traversal depth\n  -k, --top-k INTEGER   BM25 result count\n  -y, --year TEXT       Year filter\n  --format [json|text]\n  --help                Show this message and exit.", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "0ce3df65-81fd-47a9-828c-9f6025fdb001", "uuid": "39945c99-a200-4254-bb0a-7ea4eba83fa6", "timestamp": "2026-07-12T11:54:50.267Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "Usage: paper-wiki [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...\n\n  My Paper Wiki CLI.\n\nOptions:\n  --help  Show this message and exit.\n\nCommands:\n  index   Build indexes.\n  list    List papers or sections.\n  search  Search papers and content.\n---\nUsage: paper-wiki search [OPTIONS]\n\n  Search papers and content.\n\nOptions:\n  -p, --paper TEXT      arXiv ID\n  -s, --section TEXT    Section name\n  -c, --concept TEXT    Search by concept\n  -d, --dataset TEXT    Search by dataset\n  -a, --author TEXT     Search by author\n  -m, --method TEXT     Search by method\n  -f, --fuzzy TEXT      Fuzzy search\